<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Au revoir BNP Paribas</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Libre+Baskerville:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Outfit:wght@200;300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: #060910;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* ── Aurora background ── */
  .aurora {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .aurora-band {
    position: absolute;
    width: 160%;
    height: 340px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(70px);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: auroraPulse 10s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  .ab1 {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00a651 0%, #00c46a 40%, transparent 70%);
    top: 10%; left: -30%;
    animation-delay: 0s;
    opacity: 0.12;
  }
  .ab2 {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 20%, #009ee0 60%, #0066cc 100%);
    top: 30%; right: -40%;
    animation-delay: -3s;
    opacity: 0.10;
  }
  .ab3 {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00a651 0%, #009ee0 100%);
    bottom: 5%; left: 10%;
    height: 200px;
    opacity: 0.08;
    animation-delay: -6s;
  }
  @keyframes auroraPulse {
    0%   { transform: translateY(0px) scaleX(1);   opacity: var(--op, 0.12); }
    50%  { transform: translateY(30px) scaleX(1.05); }
    100% { transform: translateY(-20px) scaleX(0.96); opacity: calc(var(--op, 0.12) * 1.4); }
  }

  /* Stars */
  .stars {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 12% 18%, rgba(255,255,255,0.5) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 34% 62%, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 55% 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.4) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 73% 80%, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 88% 15%, rgba(255,255,255,0.5) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 20% 85%, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 65% 55%, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 45% 10%, rgba(255,255,255,0.6) 0%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 92% 45%, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 0%, transparent 100%);
  }

  /* ── Card ── */
  .card {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    width: min(520px, 92vw);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.035);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 0;
    backdrop-filter: blur(28px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(28px);
    overflow: hidden;
    animation: fadeUp 1s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1) both;
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 1px rgba(0,166,81,0.15),
      0 32px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.6),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(36px) scale(0.98); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
  }

  /* Glow strip at top */
  .glow-strip {
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, #00a651 30%, #009ee0 70%, transparent 100%);
    animation: glowPulse 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  @keyframes glowPulse {
    from { opacity: 0.7; }
    to   { opacity: 1; filter: brightness(1.3); }
  }

  /* Inner padding wrapper */
  .inner {
    padding: 44px 48px 40px;
  }

  /* ── Top row: tag + icon ── */
  .top-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    animation: fadeUp 1s .15s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1) both;
  }
  .tag-pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 5px 12px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,166,81,0.35);
    background: rgba(0,166,81,0.08);
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #00c46a;
  }
  .tag-dot {
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #00c46a;
    animation: blink 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50%       { opacity: 0.3; }
  }
  .card-date {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 200;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
  }

  /* ── Heading ── */
  h1 {
    font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', serif;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 5vw, 36px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.25;
    color: #f0f0ea;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    animation: fadeUp 1s .25s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1) both;
  }
  h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00c46a, #009ee0);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  /* ── Divider ── */
  .divider {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 26px 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1s .35s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1) both;
  }
  .divider-line {
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,166,81,0.4), transparent);
  }
  .divider-line.right {
    background: linear-gradient(270deg, rgba(0,158,224,0.4), transparent);
  }
  .divider-icon {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  }

  /* ── Body text ── */
  p {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(240,240,234,0.65);
    animation: fadeUp 1s .45s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1) both;
  }
  p strong {
    color: rgba(240,240,234,0.9);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* ── Signature ── */
  .sig {
    margin-top: 36px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    animation: fadeUp 1s .55s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1) both;
  }
  .sig-avatar {
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00a651 0%, #009ee0 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    color: #fff;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,166,81,0.3);
  }
  .sig-text strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: rgba(240,240,234,0.9);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .sig-text span {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 200;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: rgba(240,240,234,0.35);
  }

  /* ── Footer band ── */
  .card-footer {
    margin-top: 32px;
    padding: 14px 48px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.025);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    animation: fadeUp 1s .65s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1) both;
  }
  .footer-left {
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
  }
  .footer-right {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .fbar {
    width: 20px;
    height: 3px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }
  .fbar:nth-child(1) { background: rgba(0,166,81,0.5); width: 28px; }
  .fbar:nth-child(2) { background: rgba(0,158,224,0.4); width: 16px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="aurora">
  <div class="aurora-band ab1"></div>
  <div class="aurora-band ab2"></div>
  <div class="aurora-band ab3"></div>
</div>
<div class="stars"></div>

<div class="card">
  <div class="glow-strip"></div>

  <div class="inner">

    <div class="top-row">
      <div class="tag-pill">
        <div class="tag-dot"></div>
        Fin de mission
      </div>
      <div class="card-date">Avril 2026</div>
    </div>

    <h1>Merci pour<br>ces <em>moments précieux</em>.</h1>

    <div class="divider">
      <div class="divider-line"></div>
      <div class="divider-icon">✦</div>
      <div class="divider-line right"></div>
    </div>

    <p>
      Travailler avec vous a été un vrai <strong>plaisir</strong>.
      La bonne humeur, l'entraide et la générosité de chacun —
      c'est ce que je garderai le plus <strong>précieusement</strong>.
      J'espère sincèrement que nos chemins se recroiseront.
    </p>

    <div class="sig">
      <div class="sig-avatar">P</div>
      <div class="sig-text">
        <strong>[Prénom Nom]</strong>
        <span>Avec beaucoup de gratitude ✦</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="card-footer">
    <div class="footer-left">BNP Paribas · Au revoir</div>
    <div class="footer-right">
      <div class="fbar"></div>
      <div class="fbar"></div>
      <div class="fbar"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
